---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/?$/, "/");
---

<style>
  @import "../styles/home.css";
</style>

<Layout title="Início" activePage="home">
  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section
    class="hero-section relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-6 py-32"
  >
    <!-- Background decorative blurs -->
    <div
      class="blur-decorative-one absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="blur-decorative-two absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Tag badge -->
    <div
      class="tag-badge inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-8"
    >
      <span class="tag-badge-icon material-symbols-outlined">schedule</span>
      <span class="tag-badge-text text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest"
        >Gerenciador de Tempo</span
      >
    </div>

    <!-- Brand / Hero text -->
    <h1 class="brand-text mb-6">Orange Clockwork</h1>

    <!-- Tagline -->
    <p
      class="mb-4 max-w-2xl"
      style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.75rem); color: rgba(241,222,221,0.9); font-weight: 600;"
    >
      Domine seu tempo. Mantenha o foco.
    </p>

    <!-- Subtitle -->
    <p
      class="mb-12 max-w-xl"
      style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(241,222,221,0.5); line-height: 1.75;"
    >
      Três ferramentas de produtividade integradas para você trabalhar com mais
      eficiência e nunca mais perder o controle do seu tempo.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA Buttons -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
      <a
        href={`${base}pomodoro`}
        class="btn-pomodoro flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
      >
        <span
          class="material-symbols-outlined"
          style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">timer</span
        >
        Começar com Pomodoro
      </a>
      <a
        href={`${base}stopwatch`}
        class="flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
        style="background-color: rgba(241,222,221,0.08); color: rgba(241,222,221,0.8); font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; border: 1px solid rgba(241,222,221,0.15);"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">stopwatch</span>
        Ver Cronômetro
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Scroll indicator -->
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-1"
      style="color: rgba(241,222,221,0.25);"
    >
      <span
        class="text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase"
        style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">Explorar</span
      >
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined animate-bounce">expand_more</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURES SECTION -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-12 py-24" style="background-color: #f9f9fe;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span
          class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]"
          style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; color: var(--color-primary-container);"
          >Funcionalidades</span
        >
        <h2
          class="mt-3 font-bold tracking-tight"
          style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #191c1f; font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);"
        >
          Três Ferramentas.<br />Uma Missão.
        </h2>
        <p
          class="mt-4 max-w-lg mx-auto"
          style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #564241; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75;"
        >
          Cada ferramenta foi desenhada para uma necessidade específica de
          gestão de tempo, com uma interface limpa e sem distrações.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Bento Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
        <!-- Pomodoro Card — Featured (dark, large) -->
        <div
          class="md:col-span-7 p-8 rounded-[32px] relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col"
          style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-on-primary-container) 0%, var(--color-inverse-primary) 100%); min-height: 440px;"
        >
          <!-- Decorative ring -->
          <div
            class="absolute -right-16 -bottom-16 opacity-10 pointer-events-none"
          >
            <svg width="220" height="220" viewBox="0 0 220 220">
              <circle
                cx="110"
                cy="110"
                r="100"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#af4949"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-dasharray="6 4"></circle>
              <circle
                cx="110"
                cy="110"
                r="72"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#af4949"
                stroke-width="1"
                stroke-dasharray="3 5"></circle>
              <circle cx="110" cy="110" r="8" fill="#af4949"></circle>
              <line
                x1="110"
                y1="110"
                x2="110"
                y2="22"
                stroke="#af4949"
                stroke-width="2.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"></line>
              <line
                x1="110"
                y1="110"
                x2="162"
                y2="110"
                stroke="#af4949"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <span
            class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4"
            style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; color: rgba(255,179,176,0.5);"
            >Técnica de Foco</span
          >

          <div
            class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
            style="background-color: rgba(144,50,51,0.3);"
          >
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl"
              style="color: #ffb3b0; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;"
              >timer</span
            >
          </div>

          <h3
            class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3"
            style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #f1dedd;"
          >
            Pomodoro
          </h3>

          <p
            class="mb-6 flex-1"
            style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: rgba(241,222,221,0.55); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.75;"
          >
            A técnica de produtividade mais eficaz do mundo. Ciclos de foco
            profundo intercalados com pausas estratégicas para maximizar seu
            rendimento.
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8">
            {
              [
                "25 min de foco + pausas programadas",
                "Rastreamento de sessões do dia",
                "Gestão de tarefa atual",
                "Avanço automático entre modos",
              ].map((f) => (
                <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <span
                    class="material-symbols-outlined"
                    style="color: #97d694; font-size: 1rem; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;"
                  >
                    check_circle
                  </span>
                  <span style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: rgba(241,222,221,0.65); font-size: 0.85rem;">
                    {f}
                  </span>
                </li>
              ))
            }
          </ul>

          <a
            href={`${base}pomodoro`}
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold w-fit transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #903233, #af4949); color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem;"
          >
            Abrir Pomodoro
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1rem;"
              >arrow_forward</span
            >
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Stopwatch Card -->
        <div
          class="md:col-span-5 p-8 rounded-[32px] flex flex-col"
          style="background-color: #f3f3f8; min-height: 440px;"
        >
          <span
            class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4"
            style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; color: #564241;"
            >Medição de Tempo</span
          >

          <div
            class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
            style="background-color: rgba(76,97,108,0.12);"
          >
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl"
              style="color: #4c616c; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;"
              >stopwatch</span
            >
          </div>

          <h3
            class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3"
            style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #191c1f;"
          >
            Cronômetro
          </h3>

          <p
            class="mb-6 flex-1"
            style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #564241; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.75;"
          >
            Precisão de centésimos de segundo com registro de voltas e
            estatísticas detalhadas para análise de desempenho.
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8">
            {
              [
                "Precisão em centésimos de segundo",
                "Registro e histórico de voltas",
                "Estatísticas de melhor e última volta",
              ].map((f) => (
                <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <span
                    class="material-symbols-outlined"
                    style="color: #235d29; font-size: 1rem; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;"
                  >
                    check_circle
                  </span>
                  <span style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #564241; font-size: 0.85rem;">
                    {f}
                  </span>
                </li>
              ))
            }
          </ul>

          <a
            href={`${base}stopwatch`}
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold w-fit transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
            style="background-color: #191c1f; color: #f9f9fe; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem;"
          >
            Abrir Cronômetro
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1rem;"
              >arrow_forward</span
            >
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Countdown Card — Full Width -->
        <div
          class="md:col-span-12 p-8 rounded-[32px] flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 md:gap-16"
          style="background-color: #ededf2;"
        >
          <!-- Left -->
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col">
            <span
              class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4"
              style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; color: #564241;"
              >Temporizador</span
            >

            <div
              class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
              style="background-color: rgba(35,93,41,0.1);"
            >
              <span
                class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl"
                style="color: #235d29; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;"
                >hourglass_bottom</span
              >
            </div>

            <h3
              class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3"
              style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #191c1f;"
            >
              Contagem Regressiva
            </h3>

            <p
              style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #564241; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.75; max-width: 38rem;"
            >
              Defina um tempo personalizado ou escolha entre presets rápidos.
              Sons de alarme gerados proceduralmente avisam quando o tempo
              esgota.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Right -->
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:w-80 shrink-0">
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              {
                [
                  "Tempo personalizado (HH:MM:SS)",
                  "Presets rápidos: 15, 25, 45 e 90 min",
                  "3 tons de alarme distintos",
                  "Sons gerados via Web Audio API",
                ].map((f) => (
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span
                      class="material-symbols-outlined"
                      style="color: #235d29; font-size: 1rem; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;"
                    >
                      check_circle
                    </span>
                    <span style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #564241; font-size: 0.85rem;">
                      {f}
                    </span>
                  </li>
                ))
              }
            </ul>

            <a
              href={`${base}countdown`}
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold w-fit transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
              style="background-color: #235d29; color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem;"
            >
              Abrir Contagem Regressiva
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 1rem;"
                >arrow_forward</span
              >
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-12 py-24" style="background-color: #f3f3f8;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span
          class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]"
          style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; color: #903233;"
          >Como Funciona</span
        >
        <h2
          class="mt-3 font-bold tracking-tight"
          style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #191c1f; font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);"
        >
          A Técnica Pomodoro
        </h2>
        <p
          class="mt-4 max-w-lg mx-auto"
          style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #564241; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75;"
        >
          Desenvolvida por Francesco Cirillo nos anos 80, esta técnica usa
          intervalos de tempo para melhorar foco e produtividade de forma
          sustentável.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {
          [
            {
              icon: "task_alt",
              step: "01",
              title: "Defina a Tarefa",
              desc: "Escolha o que você vai trabalhar durante a sessão e escreva no campo de foco.",
              color: "#903233",
              bg: "rgba(144,50,51,0.08)",
            },
            {
              icon: "timer",
              step: "02",
              title: "Trabalhe 25 min",
              desc: "Concentre-se completamente na tarefa por 25 minutos sem interrupções.",
              color: "#903233",
              bg: "rgba(144,50,51,0.08)",
            },
            {
              icon: "coffee",
              step: "03",
              title: "Pausa de 5 min",
              desc: "Faça uma pausa curta para descansar a mente. Levante, alongue, respire.",
              color: "#235d29",
              bg: "rgba(35,93,41,0.08)",
            },
            {
              icon: "self_improvement",
              step: "04",
              title: "Pausa Longa",
              desc: "A cada 4 pomodoros, faça uma pausa de 15 minutos para recuperação completa.",
              color: "#235d29",
              bg: "rgba(35,93,41,0.08)",
            },
          ].map((item) => (
            <div
              class="p-6 rounded-[24px] flex flex-col"
              style="background-color: #ffffff;"
            >
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
                <div
                  class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center"
                  style={`background-color: ${item.bg};`}
                >
                  <span
                    class="material-symbols-outlined"
                    style={`color: ${item.color}; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;`}
                  >
                    {item.icon}
                  </span>
                </div>
                <span
                  class="text-4xl font-bold"
                  style={`font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: ${item.color}; opacity: 0.12;`}
                >
                  {item.step}
                </span>
              </div>
              <h4
                class="text-lg font-bold mb-2"
                style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #191c1f;"
              >
                {item.title}
              </h4>
              <p
                class="text-sm leading-relaxed"
                style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #564241;"
              >
                {item.desc}
              </p>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section
    class="px-6 md:px-12 py-28 text-center relative overflow-hidden"
    style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #150c0c 0%, #1a0d0d 100%);"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-72 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"
      style="background-color: rgba(144,50,51,0.2);"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto relative z-10">
      <span
        class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]"
        style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; color: rgba(255,179,176,0.5);"
        >Comece Agora</span
      >
      <h2
        class="mt-4 mb-4 font-bold tracking-tight"
        style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #f1dedd; font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 3rem);"
      >
        Seu tempo é o seu recurso mais valioso.
      </h2>
      <p
        class="mb-10"
        style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: rgba(241,222,221,0.45); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75;"
      >
        Escolha uma ferramenta e comece a trabalhar com mais foco e intenção a
        partir de agora.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href={`${base}pomodoro`}
          class="flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
          style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #903233, #af4949); color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(144,50,51,0.35);"
        >
          <span
            class="material-symbols-outlined"
            style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">timer</span
          >
          Iniciar Pomodoro
        </a>
        <a
          href={`${base}stopwatch`}
          class="flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
          style="background-color: rgba(241,222,221,0.08); color: rgba(241,222,221,0.7); font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; border: 1px solid rgba(241,222,221,0.12);"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">stopwatch</span>
          Cronômetro
        </a>
        <a
          href={`${base}countdown`}
          class="flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
          style="background-color: rgba(241,222,221,0.08); color: rgba(241,222,221,0.7); font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; border: 1px solid rgba(241,222,221,0.12);"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">hourglass_bottom</span>
          Contagem Regressiva
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
